Name: Google MapMaker
Description: Community additions to streets. This is much more detailed than normal Google in some locations. It is incompatioble with Streetview.

Name: Google MapMapker Hybrid
Description: Community additions to streets overlaid over Satellite imagery. This is much more detailed than normal Google in some locations. It is incompatioble with Streetview.

Name: Google Earth
Description: Earth allows access to a 3D satellite view.

Name: Google Streetview
Description: Streetview allows access to a 3D photographic panorama. It is incompatible with MapMaker layers.
